"""
google_agent/live_tutor_agents/orchestrator_registry.py
===============================================================================
V18 fixed Stage2 registry/orchestration.

Fixes the current timeout problem:
- Does NOT rerun expensive RAG when Node/sourceContextBuilder already supplied
  selectedEvidence/pageContexts/pageImages.
- Runs SelectedPageVisionAgent directly using its real Gemini Vision helpers.
- Adds checkpoint modes:
    stopAfterSelectedPageVision
    stopAfterVisualPlanner
    stopAfterBoardScene
- Adds per-agent timeout so one slow ADK/Gemini agent cannot hang the whole
  Python process silently.
- Keeps a sequential dependency spine, but runs independent planning/teaching
  branches in parallel where safe.

Rules:
- No fake fallback.
- If page images exist and selected page vision is required, Gemini Vision failure
  stops Stage2 clearly.
- PDF extracted text/chunks remain truth.
- OCR/image text is helper only.
===============================================================================
"""

